		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/03/circumventing-panopticon-transmediale-berlin.html" title="Permalink to Circumventing the Panopticon, Transmediale Berlin" rel="bookmark">Circumventing the Panopticon, Transmediale Berlin</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/03/circumventing-panopticon-transmediale-berlin.html" title="21:01" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-03-22T21:01:41+00:00" pubdate>March 22, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
