				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Last month I was on a panel dis­cus­sion at the Ber­lin Trans­me­diale con­fer­ence with <span class="caps">NSA</span> whis­tleblower Bill Bin­ney, Chelsea Man­ning rap­por­teur Alexa O’Brian, and act­iv­ist Diani Bar­reto. Here is the link to the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qxU1voSEDA">full two hour event</a>, and here is my speech:</p>
